&lt;p&gt;This is a high-impact, cross-functional role. You&#39;ll sit within the Software &amp;amp; Data Science organization and collaborate daily with experimental biologists, AI/ML researchers, software engineers, and client-facing teams.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a &lt;strong&gt;full-time, onsite role&lt;/strong&gt; in San Francisco.&lt;/p&gt;
