&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design, implement, and critically evaluate computational approaches for scRNA-seq, bulk RNA-seq, secretomics, and proteomics data including QC, normalization, batch correction, dimensionality reduction, clustering, differential expression, trajectory analysis, and multi-dataset integration.&lt;/li&gt;
